'''Thakwaash''' were [[Equine/Legends|equinoid]] biped [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Thakwaa/Legends|Thakwaa]].

==Biology and appearance==
Each Thakwaash had many different personalities, each performing some specialized function. This was their normal mental state and was not considered a [[Multiple personality disorder|psychosis]], as it would be in a [[Human/Legends|Human]]. As they grew older and developed, they usually discovered more "minds," and gradually improved upon their skill in switching between them. These personalities had various abilities and skills, behaviors, and views on life. These could include an undisciplined yet skilled [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]], a calm and polite socializer, an arrogant, elitist mind, an insane one (which only caused slight problems, since they could still switch to other "minds"), and others. This ability also helped them figure out how others would think, increasing their ability to imitate their target's writings or thought processes.<ref name="X-Wing: Wraith Squadron">''[[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron]]''</ref><ref name="X-Wing: Iron Fist">''[[X-Wing: Iron Fist]]''</ref>

They were also, on average, three times as strong as an average human male. For instance, [[Hohass Ekwesh]] was capable of killing a man weighing 100 kilograms by "casually" swinging him into a wall, one-handed, despite being considered small for his people.<ref name="X-Wing: Solo Command">''[[X-Wing: Solo Command]]''</ref> They had an average height of three [[Meter/Legends|meters]] with long manes of dark fur.<ref name="Galaxy at War" />

==History==
[[File:Thakwaash.jpg|thumb|right|150px|A Thakwaash]]
The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] gave up trying to take over their homeworld due to their unpredictable natures, as well as their size and strength.

The Thakwaash were members of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. [[Wraith Squadron]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Hohass Ekwesh]] was a Thakwaash. Ekwesh was nicknamed "Runt" because he was a mere two meters tall&mdash;small for his [[Species/Legends|species]].

